a's Blood Trail is presuming that the characters are in Colombia and Venezuela. * ''[[Excel Saga]]'': In episode 19 ("Menchi's Great adventure"), Menchi and a young rich girl go to Colombia and drink coffee * ''[[Hellsing]]'': In OVA 7, is told that Bernadotte's Great Father died in Colombia
